df <- read.csv("data/listings.csv")
target_cols <- c("host_location",
                 "zipcode",
                 "bedrooms",
                 "bathrooms",
                 "price",
                 "neighbourhood_cleansed",
                 "latitude",
                 "longitude")
df <- data[, target_cols]
colnames(df)
[1] "host_location"          "zipcode"                "bedrooms"              
[4] "bathrooms"              "price"                  "neighbourhood_cleansed"
[7] "latitude"               "longitude"             
colSums(is.na.data.frame(df))
         host_location                zipcode               bedrooms              bathrooms 
                     0                      0                      0                      0 
                 price neighbourhood_cleansed               latitude              longitude 
                     0                      0                      0                      0 
nrow(df)
[1] 1180
df <- df[complete.cases(df),]
nrow(df)
[1] 1180
plot(df$latitude, df$longitude)
